  <name>Bitwig Studio</name>
  <summary>Modern music production and performance for Windows, macOS, and Linux</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Bitwig Studio is a digital audio workstation (DAW) that inspires you to take greater control of your music,
    giving you access to every aspect of your production. Streamline your creative process and quickly evolve your
    ideas into complete songs, tracks, and compositions. Record and arrange, improvise and perform, or do it all at once.
    Design sounds. Build instruments. <em>Make music.</em></p>
  </description>
